Successfully developed and launched a mobile application for a large retail client, which received positive feedback from both the client and end-users.
Created a customized e-commerce platform for a small business, resulting in a 30% increase in online sales within the first quarter.
Led a team of developers in the implementation of a cloud-based solution for a major healthcare provider, resulting in improved data security and efficiency.
I am constantly seeking opportunities to improve my skills and stay up-to-date with the latest trends in software development. I have completed various courses and certifications in cloud computing, database management, and Agile methodologies.

